works.description: Hello Kitty is the epitome of a luxurious fashion statement and is treasured by many female fans throughout the globe. The fictional character that was designed by Yuko Shimizu was introduced in 1976 and since is selling many lavish products across the globe. Hello Kitty has been in fashion for a long time now, with kids to middle aged women to animals. Hello Kitty bags, shoes, toys, clothes, tattoos and many more items are high in quantity in the markets. Sanrio, a Japanese company that owns the character, earns over $1 billion annually in sales
